parameters.name: Windplot_cold_asc_080
parameters.description: Wind vector map, 80 km, Cylindrical projection, Ascending orbit phase, Cold side. This variable is a 'virtual' variable that is computed using the function wind_plot (see https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/pub/software/cdawlib/source/virtual_funcs.pro) on the with inputs of the variables ['Ucold_P9_ascend', 'Vcold_P9_ascend']. Note that not all COMPONENTS are time series and so their values are not available from the HAPI interface. They are accessible from the raw CDF files, however.
